OL,3,CMayoral election delay is
OL,4,C'authoritarian', ex-Labour MP claims
OL,6,FLloyd Russell-Moyle told ITV
OL,7,FMeridian's The Last Word that he
OL,8,Fbelieved Labour had realised they were
OL,9,F"not going to get their way" so had
OL,10,F"pulled the elections".
OL,12,F"The government has completely botched
OL,13,Fthis up...it's authoritarianism in the
OL,14,FLabour Party," he added.
OL,16,FMr Russell-Moyle, who represented
OL,17,FBrighton Kemptown in Parliament from
OL,18,F2017 to 2024, announced his defection
OL,19,Ffrom Labour to the Green Party last
OL,20,Fmonth.
