OL,3,CMayoral election delay is
OL,4,C'authoritarian', ex-Labour MP claims
OL,6,FMinisters announced last week that
OL,7,Fthey planned to delay the inaugural
OL,8,Fmayoral contests in 'Hampshire and the
OL,9,FSolent' and 'Sussex and Brighton' from
OL,10,F2026 until 2028.
OL,12,FReform UK's deputy leader, Richard
OL,13,FTice, told The Last Word his party was
OL,14,Fconsidering legal action against the
OL,15,Fgovernment over the election delay. Mr
OL,16,FTice added: "It's a scandalous outrage
OL,17,Fdeliberately designed to prevent
OL,18,FReform from winning."
