OL,3,CMayoral election delay is
OL,4,C'authoritarian', ex-Labour MP claims
OL,6,FLabour's Jessica Toale denied that,
OL,7,Fsaying: "Reform in local government
OL,8,Fhas been a shambles, why would we be
OL,9,Frunning scared from that?"
OL,11,FDefending the government's decision to
OL,12,Fdelay the elections, Ms Toale said:
OL,13,F"We are committed to devolution and we
OL,14,Fwant to make local government as
OL,15,Fefficient and as effective as possible
OL,16,F` and that takes time."
OL,18,FThe Bournemouth West MP admitted
OL,19,Fintroducing new mayors "had proved
OL,20,Fcomplicated" but said Labour "wanted
OL,21,Fto get it right".
