OL,3,CMayoral election delay is
OL,4,C'authoritarian', ex-Labour MP claims
OL,6,F"These areas are getting around #200
OL,7,Fmillion a year in support for housing,
OL,8,Ffor skills, and for investments in the
OL,9,Finfrastructure they need. We recognise
OL,10,Fthat, yes they're delayed, but we want
OL,11,Fto make sure that that transition is
OL,12,Fsmooth," Ms Toale added.
OL,14,FShadow Local Government Minister, Paul
OL,15,FHolmes, told ITV's The Last Word the
OL,16,Fdecision would "deny democracy" and
OL,17,F"should be reversed".
