OL,3,CMayoral election delay is
OL,4,C'authoritarian', ex-Labour MP claims
OL,6,FThe Conservative MP for Hamble Valley
OL,7,Fadded: "This is Labour running scared
OL,8,Fbut what's more annoying for my
OL,9,Fconstituents is the money wasted, the
OL,10,Fmoney they're going to lose because of
OL,11,Fthis delay, because of the
OL,12,Fgovernment's own inaction."
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat Alison Bennett
OL,15,Fdescribed the delay as "absolutely
OL,16,Fshambolic" at a time when "people's
OL,17,Ftrust in politics and politicians is
OL,18,Fso low, the idea the government can
OL,19,Funilaterally cancel elections only
OL,20,Fundermines that."
