OL,3,CMayoral election delay is
OL,4,C'authoritarian', ex-Labour MP claims
OL,6,FCounty council elections in Essex,
OL,7,FEast and West Sussex and Hampshire -
OL,8,Fdelayed from earlier this year ` are
OL,9,Fnow expected to go ahead in May 2026.
OL,11,FThe introduction of elected mayors in
OL,12,Fthe South of England was a key part of
OL,13,FLabour's devolution agenda, and is
OL,14,Fhappening at the same time as changes
OL,15,Fto local councils.
OL,17,FITV Meridian's monthly political
OL,18,Fprogramme, The Last Word, is on ITV1
OL,19,Fat 10.45pm on Thursday, 11 December
OL,20,F2025. Watch the full episode on ITVX
OL,21,Fand YouTube.
